@startuml
title UC-02. Зарегистрировать endpoint сервиса

actor "Специалист поддержки" as Support
participant "Monitoring API" as API
participant "Monitoring Config Module" as Config
database "Monitoring DB" as DB

Support -> API: POST /api/v1/services/{serviceId}/endpoints
API -> Config: addEndpoint(serviceId, request)

Config -> DB: SELECT service WHERE id = serviceId
DB --> Config: service found

Config -> Config: validate endpoint url
Config -> Config: validate method, timeout, interval

Config -> DB: INSERT endpoint
DB --> Config: endpoint_id

Config --> API: created endpoint
API --> Support: 201 Created + endpoint_id

@enduml